profile:
Residential / Commercial Window & Gutter Cleaning Services in the GTA

With over 15 years + experience, Jessie's Spotless Window Cleaning Services provides unmatched window & gutter cleaning services through fully qualified trained window cleaners and site supervisors.

We make sure that the home owners, building managers, and supervisors are left with a lasting impression based on our service. All of our workers are fully trained, bondable, certified with WSIB, Fall Arrest & Working At Heights Certificates. We carry Liability Insurance Coverage of $5,000,000 for your protection and ours & We use 100% natural cleaning products.

Our service ranges from residential homes to commercial buildings/condos. The services we provide is Interior/ Exterior Window Cleaning, High Rise, Low Rise Window Cleaning, Gutter Cleaning, Gutter Guard Install, Chandelier Cleaning, Janitorial Cleaning, Carpet Cleaning, Power Washing, Caulking, Festive Lights Install & Post Construction Clean.

profile:
Experience 5-star customer service done right. We provide our clients with the best professional and high-quality window cleaning, power washing, and gutter cleaning services. Our technicians will show up to your home or business ready to carry out your service call with professional equipment and tools.

Exterior window cleaning is done by top-notch carbon fiber, water-fed pole, specialized squeegee, and filtered water to ensure shine of the windows. Our interior window cleaning service is done by hand – we use the classic applicator and squeegee method. We can also clean skylights, solariums and screens to make your property shine.

profile:
Hi there and welcome to my page! I am a third year student, studying synthetic biology at Western University. During the summers, I run a window cleaning business with College Pro. This is my own small business, and my whole team consists of students, like me. Our goal is to provide you quick and efficient service and with a level of quality and customer service which you have never seen before.

We service residential homes doing interior and exterior window cleaning, eavestrough cleaning, siding cleaning, and even concrete and deck powerwashing and sealing. We would love to have the opportunity to do some work for you this summer, so please don't hesitate to reach out for a free, no obligation quote, or to chat if you have any questions or inquiries! 

We look forward to meeting you!
